intend, expect, observe
  intention
    only apply to writeable remote subjects
  observation
    only apply to readable remote subjects
  expectation
    can apply to any
    if remote subject: should only be updated after write to remote was successful
    can be divided into warning and critical expectations
  apply: intention -> expectation
  fix: expectation -> observation
  observe: updates observation
  intend: sets intention
  expect: sets expectation

